THE PROCESS
How It Works
1. Schedule Online
Fill out the pickup form and tell us what e-waste you have.
2. We Come to You
We arrive at your Boulder-area address and collect your electronics door to door.
3. Recycled or Reused
All e-waste is taken to our partnered processing facility for responsible recycling. When items have reuse potential, we aim to repurpose them before sending them to the e-waste processing site.

